description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Gaston purrs with a rating of 77, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 385, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 5 for East, Stringalong for South, and Box for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60775-85740-0.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [385 Votes, Hall of Fame]
